d to be taken up - as I said in the chickens run, see, and then - as time goes along you were - you go collecting eggs, you're responsible on the - responsibility on the eggs see. Well father used to check on them, because he was working night shift, he k
new what was coming - what was in the sheds - now what was - what was brought in - at night you see, he used to check it see. So - anyhow we had our own particular jobs to do.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 What would your brother John have to do, did they have particular jobs to do, did Gert have a particular job or Mary or Mag?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 
Well - the boys, they had - they done most of the particular - the small jobs in the house because - once the girls come of age, and left school - mother sent them out to service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 So they weren't home then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 No. See - all little odd jobs rested on the boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 So the boys had to do the jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Do you remember the girls doing any of these little jobs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh no, only just around the housework while they were home that's all. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 How long did you go on doing these jobs around the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh 'til I started work. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Did the older children help the younger children with things they found difficult, like dressing or eating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Or look after the children in any way? Did you have to look after the younger ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 
Ah well - mother wouldn't trust - well we were bit - bit rebels in them days, the younger child with - with us you see so - she'd either put - out with a relativ
e - if she had to go anywhere she either put it with - take - take the child with her or leave it with a neighbour or something like that for to look after the child.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 What about helping them to eat at the table or anything like that, do you remember helping the younger children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 No, mother always fed the younger ones first before we - before we had ours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Did the younger children help the older children in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time in your school-days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh yes. Oh yes. Yes. Oh after tea, about six. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Did your mother or anyone else put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 At what age did you put yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh well I suppose - really I think I was about six or seven I think, we used to undress and dress ourselves and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Did you share the bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Or the bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Yes, brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Which one would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Johnnie.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 You and John shared the bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Can you remember how the family slept, what the sleeping arrangements were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Well - I think - you'd better knock it off a minute.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Your father and mother had one bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 One bedroom, and - and the baby, the youngest at them days, and I think and the - being quite small
 in Princes Street - we all had our - muck in together you know, you know what I mean, sleep one with the other you see, but later years of course there's only Johnnie and myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 What about in Princes Street, would there be more than one bed in your bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 
No - the bed I slept in was only enough room for - a four foot bed. So there was two of us there. Then mother had a - a - I believe mother had a - had one the other room, one room, and there was - in the larger room there was - I think there
 was two beds, and those two beds was split up between the remainder o - the children.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 What room did you bath in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh in the scullery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 How often did you bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 When did you have clean clothes to put on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Once a week - well - mostly once a week but - if we got rather dirty, we - we'd have to change.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh in - in the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Were there any occasions when you ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Not to my knowledge, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 On the fire. In - in the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 What sort of cooking equipment was it? A range or a gas stove?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 No, no, a coal fire. Coal fire and - and the old - iron - iron pots you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 There was no oven was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 There was a oven, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 On the side, like a range, a coal range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 That's right. Yes. Well it wasn't - it wasn't classed as a range, just the - the coal fire and the oven on the side see, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 When was breakfast eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh well - oh about eight or half past I suppose, but - when we started school we had to be in school by nine.
\par 
