\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh well - the elder - the elder - eldest child - would be those that would 
be going to school, they'd have their breakfast first and - what was left of the remainder of the family, well they'd eat after we'd gone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 What about your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Well he'd be in work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 He'd have had his would he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Yes, he goes out at six see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Who would have breakfast with him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Mother - mother get up, mother get up. On times but - it just depends - sometimes she'd get up and sometimes she didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Would he have breakfast on his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Would she have breakfast with him or with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Oh he - she'd get him - if she got up she'd get him off to work first.
