ng like that. And then teatime well - jam butt}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4072492\charrsid3559264 er}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 
 perhaps we'd have jelly and custard or something like that. Or fruit. But that was not - that was very of - not very often at all.
