No, I don't believe so. 'Cos - mother was very strict on - on food. She shared it all out, she had so much - so many to herself come out of that lot, she shared it out. One wouldn't get no more than the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Your father wouldn't have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 No.
