Mostly, yes, it just depends - perhaps one of the family'd be out and mother wouldn't wait for them to come back, the - that particular one to come back in so we'd get on with our meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Did you always have the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Yes.
