Well - father - there was father, mother - there was Johnnie, I think there was myself - and the - Mary, and we all go down - went around, you see - in the age - like in the age group as you go down. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 What about the youngest children?
