\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Yes, I think we were. 'Cos - mother was so preoccupied naturally - to bother as long as you were out of s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4072492\charrsid3559264 i}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 ght.
