\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 No, the schoolmaster - if there was anyth
ing wrong - that the schoolmaster didn't approve of - he always used to come - he'd always come up to the house. Yes. Not only our place mind - any - any place, where perhaps - pupil be - you know, get out of hand, he couldn't control him and one thing an
d another, or - give him - there - there was no - there was no school reports in them days, if a boy - if his report was bad well - they - you'd have it on your report but - if he find out that you were - you were bad in one certain -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Did the schoolmaster ever come up to your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12139752 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 But you don't know why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10954091 RM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14754656\charrsid3559264 
Oh yes. That was time when I was taken bad - I'd be - been in poor health for a long time, it was not feeling up to the mark you know, and of course I was gradually gong down a b
it you know in my lessons and he - and he did come up - and - and then when my granny died, and I had - then I had pleurisy, it was - that was coming on gradually you see, and - then he came up to find out why I wasn't in school, and then - when I got bet
ter - and - he found \endash 
 he got my - the - my school books out but they work like that and he'd - I was supposed to have gone then - in a few weeks time go for exam in the - higher grade at Ferndale. And I went up, though I had lot - I lost a lot of work, but
 I managed to pull through. But I - in the end it was a waste of time because - I - I couldn't go on. I had to come out and go to the pits.
